    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212310/extras/64aee5a62f409d19abf63347ab736723.avif?t=1762047078\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212310/extras_big/64aee5a62f409d19abf63347ab736723.webp?t=1762047078 width=1600 height=426 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212310/extras/2c43576cc74e30dc316042c13a822b6b.avif?t=1762047078\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212310/extras_big/2c43576cc74e30dc316042c13a822b6b.avif?t=1762047078 width=800 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212310/extras/4b9f25781e2c579916ebcbd26e1a8f1f.poster.avif?t=1762047078\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212310/extras/4b9f25781e2c579916ebcbd26e1a8f1f.webm?t=1762047078\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212310/extras/4b9f25781e2c579916ebcbd26e1a8f1f.mp4?t=1762047078\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The  climate has reached its breaking point, </strong>with increasingly <strong>unstable</strong> weather patterns<strong> </strong>each season,<strong> </strong>causing <strong>widespread fear </strong>and <strong>destruction </strong>across the <strong>Valley.</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The <strong>Project Storm Initiative</strong> is seeking recruits to <strong>support the community</strong> and <strong>assist with their mission</strong> of reducing the catastrophic impact of nature's fury. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this <strong>solo/co-op action-adventure sim,</strong> take the wheel as a <strong>rookie Storm Chaser</strong> for the <strong>Project Storm Initiative</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212310/extras/5fa277937f5f3901f28a95ac36f765d6.poster.avif?t=1762047078\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212310/extras/5fa277937f5f3901f28a95ac36f765d6.webm?t=1762047078\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212310/extras/5fa277937f5f3901f28a95ac36f765d6.mp4?t=1762047078\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Complete contracts</strong> amid <strong>nature’s most powerful Superstorms</strong>, including <strong>Tornadoes</strong>, <strong>Lightning</strong> <strong>Storms</strong> and <strong>Typhoons</strong>. Rise through the ranks in <strong>3 thrilling career modes</strong> to become a <strong>Legendary Storm Chaser</strong>.    </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212310/extras/09d9750bec40fb06e5871694653ab493.avif?t=1762047078\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212310/extras_big/09d9750bec40fb06e5871694653ab493.avif?t=1762047078 width=800 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212310/extras/17b13111e85d98f6f7ca7efead70d809.avif?t=1762047078\" width=616 height=180 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Choose between 3 career paths</strong>, each with <strong>distinctive contacts</strong>, <strong>equipment</strong>, <strong>gear</strong>, and <strong>play</strong> <strong>styles</strong> as well as <strong>support</strong> from <strong>local legends. </strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Rapid Responder,</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Road Technician,</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Storm Interceptor,</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Contracts can range from <strong>rescuing</strong> <strong>stranded civilians and animals</strong>, <strong>clearing</strong> <strong>damaged/debris-laden</strong> roads, <strong>activating sirens</strong>, and <strong>deploying</strong> Storm Chasing <strong>equipment</strong> to collect <strong>critical storm data.</strong> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212310/extras/d61ce5056711de337a0f485377b6b588.avif?t=1762047078\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212310/extras_big/d61ce5056711de337a0f485377b6b588.avif?t=1762047078 width=800 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212310/extras/fe78a4541dc388d4c579fbeadb5d8339.poster.avif?t=1762047078\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212310/extras/fe78a4541dc388d4c579fbeadb5d8339.webm?t=1762047078\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212310/extras/fe78a4541dc388d4c579fbeadb5d8339.mp4?t=1762047078\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The ultimate chase begins in the fictitious plains of <strong>Wyndham Valley</strong>. <strong>Discover</strong> <strong>vast farmlands</strong>, <strong>sprawling valleys</strong>, and <strong>provincial rural towns</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each map presents unique <strong>environmental</strong> <strong>dangers</strong> and <strong>hazards</strong> for <strong>tactical</strong> and <strong>dynamic</strong> <strong>gameplay.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212310/extras/f0ffb41da77b1f9dbb0ba38daacfcc41.avif?t=1762047078\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212310/extras_big/f0ffb41da77b1f9dbb0ba38daacfcc41.avif?t=1762047078 width=800 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212310/extras/3f6729ced85bcfd46fc0f4e59ad78669.poster.avif?t=1762047078\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212310/extras/3f6729ced85bcfd46fc0f4e59ad78669.webm?t=1762047078\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212310/extras/3f6729ced85bcfd46fc0f4e59ad78669.mp4?t=1762047078\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Enhance your pursuit with the Storm HQ</strong> located in the South of <strong>Wyndham Valley</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Player's Storm HQ is designed to <strong>support the ultimate chase</strong> against the storm.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Enhance and expand</strong> your Storm HQ with <strong>specialized upgrades</strong> and <strong>facilities</strong> such as <strong>storage warehouses, shelters and garages</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212310/extras/51208add9a953219840f2c7cd5b42339.avif?t=1762047078\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212310/extras_big/51208add9a953219840f2c7cd5b42339.avif?t=1762047078 width=800 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212310/extras/6edbf8351d9bd69a0c9f8a350d83d5cb.poster.avif?t=1762047078\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212310/extras/6edbf8351d9bd69a0c9f8a350d83d5cb.webm?t=1762047078\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212310/extras/6edbf8351d9bd69a0c9f8a350d83d5cb.mp4?t=1762047078\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>Navigate</strong> <strong>the maps</strong> amid <strong>immersive</strong>, <strong>unpredictable</strong> <strong>Superstorms</strong> that cause <strong>widespread</strong> <strong>damage</strong> and <strong>destruction.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each storm type and intensity presents its own set of <strong>challenges</strong> in a <strong>reactive environment.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212310/extras/bf5415aae603ab5276942298da525ecf.avif?t=1762047078\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212310/extras_big/bf5415aae603ab5276942298da525ecf.avif?t=1762047078 width=800 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212310/extras/34bcd1caf634cf9c407e0410aeb59784.poster.avif?t=1762047078\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212310/extras/34bcd1caf634cf9c407e0410aeb59784.webm?t=1762047078\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212310/extras/34bcd1caf634cf9c407e0410aeb59784.mp4?t=1762047078\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>Supply </strong>and <strong>armor</strong> your ideal <strong>Storm Chaser Vehicle/s</strong> with <strong>specialized</strong> <strong>Storm</strong> <strong>Gear</strong>, <strong>armor</strong> and <strong>upgrades</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212310/extras/cbf83c613ee69c2a91c4e134fa19bc53.avif?t=1762047078\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212310/extras_big/cbf83c613ee69c2a91c4e134fa19bc53.avif?t=1762047078 width=800 height=60 /></span><strong>Play solo</strong> or <strong>join friends online</strong> in a <strong>co-operative multiplayer adventure</strong>. <strong>Join forces </strong>with<strong> </strong>your<strong> cohort</strong> to <strong>combine unique player roles</strong> and <strong>skills</strong> to <strong>quickly</strong> rise through the ranks to become <strong>legendary Storm Chasers</strong>.    </p>",
